songs.title: L.A. Baby (Where Dreams Are Made Of)

L.A, L.A, baby
(She's a)
L.A, L.A, baby
(You're my)
L.A, L.A, baby
(She's a)
L.A, L.A, baby

[Verse 1]
Driving down the highway with her
Californ-i-a breeze in my hair
Yeah, yeah!
Yeah, yeah!
Yeah, yeah!

[Verse 2]
Out on your vacation, baby
That's my destination, see you there
Yeah, yeah!
Yeah, yeah!
Yeah, yeah!

[Pre-Chorus]
Here we GO!
So now let's GO!
You gotta, GO! GO!
Bring it on!

[Chorus]
The two of us tonight
We can make it last forever
We're in the neon lights
It's just you and me together
Hollywood is the time
The stars are shining
For you and me tonight in this city
Where dreams are made of
Where dreams are made of

One on one, the night is ours
I'm on my way
Yeah Yeah! Yeah Yeah! Yeah Yeah!
We can do whatever
You can pick a place
And tell me what to say!
Yeah Yeah! Yeah Yeah! Yeah Yeah!

Bring it on!
